dict.string: Adds Fake Ambient Light Sensor (for storing brightness level)
Enables Brightness Control (Keys Fn+F8 and Fn+F9)
Enables Sleep/Clamshell Mode when closing the Lid
Fixes instant wake issue when entering Sleep Mode
Restricts _DSM to XDSM rename to macOS
Drop CpuPm (enable for generating SSDT-PM.aml but disable afterwards)
Drop Cpu0Ist (enable for generating SSDT-PM.aml but disable afterwards)
change _CRS to XCRS, pair with SSDT-HPET
change _OSIF to XSIF (to avoid match against XOSI patch)
change _OSI to XOSI, pair with SSDT-XOSI.aml
change _PTS to ZPTS (1, N), pair with SSDT-PTSWAK.aml
change _WAK to ZWAK (1, N), pair with SSDT-PTSWAK.aml
XCPM for Ivy Bridge. macOS 10.15.7 - 11.3 by 5T33Z0, pair with SSDT-XCPM.aml
